==Description==

The [[File:Spreadsheet_StyleItalic.svg|24px]] '''Spreadsheet StyleItalic''' tool toggles the contents of selected cells to/from italic.

==Usage==

# Make sure there is an active [[Spreadsheet_CreateSheet|spreadsheet]].
# Select one or more cells.
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[File:Spreadsheet_StyleItalic.svg|16px]] [[Spreadsheet_StyleItalic|Italic Text]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|Spreadsheet → Styles → [[File:Spreadsheet_StyleItalic.svg|16px]] Italic Text}} option from the menu.
#* Use the keyboard shortcut: {{KEY|Ctrl}}+{{KEY|I}}. {{Version|1.1}}


